<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>WC2026 Elo Engine</title>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0b1411; --panel:#11201b; --panel2:#152a22; --line:#25382f;
  --chalk:#edebe0; --muted:#8ba095; --muted2:#5f7268;
  --gold:#e8b24a; --gold-dim:#3a2f17;
  --pos:#4ec46a; --pos-bg:#11331c; --neg:#d2604f; --neg-bg:#33160f;
  --mono:ui-monospace,"SF Mono",Menlo,Consolas,"Liberation Mono",monospace;
  --sans:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,system-ui,sans-serif;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--chalk);font-family:var(--sans);-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%}
body{padding:0 0 70px;line-height:1.45}
.wrap{max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 14px}
header{padding:18px 0 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);margin-bottom:14px}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.brand h1{font-size:20px;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin:0;font-weight:800}
.brand .mk{color:var(--gold);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid var(--gold-dim);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px}
.sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:12.5px;margin-top:5px}
.sub a{color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px dotted var(--gold-dim)}

/* tabs */
nav.tabs{display:flex;gap:2px;position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:#0a120f;border-top:1px solid var(--line);z-index:50}
nav.tabs button{flex:1;background:none;border:0;color:var(--muted2);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.3px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:11px 2px 13px;cursor:pointer}
nav.tabs button.on{color:var(--gold)}
nav.tabs button .ic{display:block;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:2px;font-family:var(--mono);font-weight:400}
.view{display:none}.view.on{display:block}

label.fld{display:block;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.6px;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 4px}
select,input{width:100%;background:var(--panel);color:var(--chalk);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:9px 10px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:14px;-webkit-appearance:none}
select:focus,input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--gold)}
.row{display:flex;gap:8px}.row>*{flex:1;min-width:0}

.seg{display:flex;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden}
.seg button{flex:1;background:var(--panel);border:0;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:600;font-size:12.5px;padding:8px 4px;cursor:pointer}
.seg button.on{background:var(--gold);color:#1a1206}
.mt{margin-top:14px}.mt8{margin-top:8px}

.panel{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:14px;margin-top:14px}
.panel h3{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);font-weight:700}

/* W/D/L */
.wdl{display:flex;gap:8px;text-align:center}
.wdl>div{flex:1;background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:11px 4px}
.wdl .lab{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--muted)}
.wdl .big{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:25px;font-weight:700;margin:3px 0 1px;letter-spacing:-1px}
.wdl .fo{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted2)}
.wdl .home .big{color:var(--gold)} .wdl .away .big{color:var(--chalk)}

.statline{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.statline:last-child{border-bottom:0}
.statline .k{color:var(--muted)}

/* score grid */
.grid-wrap{overflow-x:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch}
table.sg{border-collapse:collapse;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;margin:0 auto}
table.sg th,table.sg td{width:30px;height:26px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #0a120f}
table.sg th{color:var(--muted);font-weight:400}
table.sg caption{caption-side:top;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;padding-bottom:6px}
table.sg td{color:var(--chalk);background:var(--panel2)}
table.sg td.peak{outline:2px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:-2px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:700}
.axis{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;text-align:center;margin-top:4px}

.cs-list{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px 14px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px}
.cs-list .ln{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:3px 0}
.cs-list .ln .s{color:var(--gold)}

/* value */
.vtable{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px}
.vtable th{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--muted);text-align:right;padding:4px 5px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);font-weight:600}
.vtable th:first-child{text-align:left}
.vtable td{padding:5px;text-align:right;border-bottom:1px solid #0e1a15}
.vtable td:first-child{text-align:left;color:var(--muted)}
.vtable input{padding:5px 6px;font-size:12.5px;text-align:right}
.badge{display:inline-block;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;min-width:54px;text-align:center}
.badge.pos{background:var(--pos-bg);color:var(--pos);border:1px solid #1d5230}
.badge.neg{background:var(--neg-bg);color:var(--neg);border:1px solid #5a2418}
.badge.zero{color:var(--muted2)}

.btn{background:var(--panel2);color:var(--chalk);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:9px 12px;font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:600;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer}
.btn.gold{background:var(--gold);color:#1a1206;border-color:var(--gold)}
.btn.ghost{background:none}
.btn.sm{padding:5px 9px;font-size:12px}
.btn.danger{color:var(--neg);border-color:#5a2418}

/* ratings table */
table.rt{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12.5px}
table.rt th{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px;color:var(--muted);text-align:left;padding:6px 5px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);font-weight:600;cursor:pointer}
table.rt td{padding:6px 5px;border-bottom:1px solid #0e1a15;font-family:var(--mono)}
table.rt td.nm{font-family:var(--sans)}
table.rt input.eloin{width:62px;padding:4px 6px;font-size:12.5px;text-align:right}
.flag{font-size:10px}.flag.v{color:var(--pos)}.flag.e{color:var(--muted2)}
.gtag{display:inline-block;width:18px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--gold);font-size:11px}
.conf{color:var(--muted2);font-size:11px}

/* groups */
.gcard{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:9px;padding:11px 12px;margin-top:10px}
.gcard h4{margin:0 0 7px;font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:.5px}
.gcard .tline{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:3px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #0e1a15}
.gcard .tline:last-child{border-bottom:0}
.gcard .tline .e{color:var(--muted)}

/* results log */
.hist{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px}
.hist .h{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #0e1a15;gap:8px}
.hist .h .res{color:var(--chalk)}
.hist .h .dl{color:var(--muted)}
.hist .h .dl .up{color:var(--pos)}.hist .h .dl .dn{color:var(--neg)}
.empty{color:var(--muted2);font-size:13px;text-align:center;padding:18px 0}
.note{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);background:var(--panel);border:1px dashed var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 12px;margin-top:14px}
.note b{color:var(--chalk)}
details{margin-top:12px}summary{cursor:pointer;color:var(--gold);font-size:13px;font-weight:600}
details p,details li{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.55}
.range{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-top:10px}
.range input[type=range]{flex:1;padding:0}
.range .val{font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--gold);min-width:46px;text-align:right;font-size:13px}
.hr{height:1px;background:var(--line);margin:14px 0}
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:78px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--gold);color:#1a1206;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;padding:9px 16px;border-radius:20px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .25s;pointer-events:none;z-index:60}
.toast.show{opacity:1}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <header>
    <div class="brand"><h1>Floodlight</h1><span class="mk">WC&nbsp;2026 · Elo</span></div>
    <div class="sub">Elo &rarr; Poisson model · live recalculation · value vs your Betfair prices. Seed ratings (8 Jun 2026) mirror <a href="https://www.footballratings.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">eloratings.net</a>.</div>
  </header>

  <!-- MATCH LAB -->
  <section id="v-lab" class="view on">
    <div class="row">
      <div><label class="fld">Team A (home side)</label><select id="teamA"></select></div>
      <div><label class="fld">Team B</label><select id="teamB"></select></div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt8">
      <div><label class="fld">Venue</label>
        <div class="seg" id="venueSeg">
          <button data-v="N" class="on">Neutral</button>
          <button data-v="A">A home</button>
          <button data-v="B">B home</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div><label class="fld">Stage</label>
        <div class="seg" id="stageSeg">
          <button data-s="group" class="on">Group</button>
          <button data-s="ko">Knockout</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Result probability</h3>
      <div class="wdl">
        <div class="home"><div class="lab" id="lblA">A win</div><div class="big" id="pW">–</div><div class="fo" id="foW"></div></div>
        <div class="draw"><div class="lab">Draw</div><div class="big" id="pD">–</div><div class="fo" id="foD"></div></div>
        <div class="away"><div class="lab" id="lblB">B win</div><div class="big" id="pL">–</div><div class="fo" id="foL"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div id="koLine" style="display:none" class="mt8"></div>
      <div class="mt8">
        <div class="statline"><span class="k">Expected goals (&lambda;)</span><span id="lamLine"></span></div>
        <div class="statline"><span class="k">Supremacy</span><span id="supLine"></span></div>
        <div class="statline"><span class="k">Elo diff (venue-adj)</span><span id="drLine"></span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Scoreline map</h3>
      <div class="grid-wrap"><div id="sgrid"></div></div>
      <div class="axis">columns = B goals &nbsp;·&nbsp; rows = A goals &nbsp;·&nbsp; gold = most likely</div>
      <div class="hr"></div>
      <div class="cs-list" id="csList"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Goals &amp; BTTS markets</h3>
      <div id="ouBox"></div>
      <div class="statline"><span class="k">BTTS — Yes</span><span id="bttsY"></span></div>
      <div class="statline"><span class="k">BTTS — No</span><span id="bttsN"></span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Value finder — enter your back odds</h3>
      <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:8px">
        <div><label class="fld">Commission %</label><input id="comm" type="number" step="0.5" value="2"></div>
        <div><label class="fld">O/U line</label>
          <select id="ouLine"><option>0.5</option><option>1.5</option><option selected>2.5</option><option>3.5</option><option>4.5</option></select>
        </div>
      </div>
      <table class="vtable">
        <thead><tr><th>Market</th><th>Model</th><th>Your odds</th><th>EV</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody id="valBody"></tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="note" style="margin-top:10px">EV is per &pound;1 back stake, net of commission on winnings. <b style="color:var(--pos)">Green = +EV</b> at your price. Fair odds shown in the Model column.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GROUPS -->
  <section id="v-groups" class="view">
    <div class="note">Live group tables ranked by current Elo. As you log results, ratings shift and groups re-sort.</div>
    <div id="groupsBox"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- RATINGS -->
  <section id="v-ratings" class="view">
    <div class="row">
      <input id="searchT" placeholder="search team…">
      <button class="btn sm" id="addTeam">+ Add</button>
    </div>
    <div class="note mt8"><span class="flag v">✓</span> verified 8 Jun · <span class="flag e">~</span> estimate — edit any value, it saves instantly. Tap a header to sort.</div>
    <div style="overflow-x:auto" class="mt8">
      <table class="rt">
        <thead><tr><th data-sort="rank">#</th><th data-sort="name">Team</th><th data-sort="group">Grp</th><th data-sort="elo" style="text-align:right">Elo</th><th></th></tr></thead>
        <tbody id="ratBody"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <button class="btn ghost danger sm mt" id="resetRat">Reset ratings to seed</button>
  </section>

  <!-- RESULTS -->
  <section id="v-results" class="view">
    <div class="panel" style="margin-top:0">
      <h3>Auto-sync results</h3>
      <button class="btn gold" id="syncBtn" style="width:100%">⟳ Sync results from API-Football</button>
      <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-top:11px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)"><input type="checkbox" id="hostAdv" checked style="width:auto"> Give hosts (USA / Canada / Mexico) home advantage</label>
      <div class="note" id="syncNote" style="margin-top:11px">Pulls finished World Cup fixtures and recalculates Elo in date order, skipping anything already logged. Works once deployed to Netlify with your API-Football key set (see README).</div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Log a played match (manual)</h3>
      <div class="row"><div><label class="fld">Home</label><select id="rHome"></select></div><div><label class="fld">Away</label><select id="rAway"></select></div></div>
      <div class="row mt8">
        <div><label class="fld">Home goals</label><input id="rHg" type="number" min="0" value="0"></div>
        <div><label class="fld">Away goals</label><input id="rAg" type="number" min="0" value="0"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row mt8">
        <div><label class="fld">Match weight (K)</label>
          <select id="rK"><option value="60" selected>World Cup finals (60)</option><option value="50">Continental final (50)</option><option value="40">WC qualifier (40)</option><option value="30">Other tourney (30)</option><option value="20">Friendly (20)</option></select>
        </div>
        <div><label class="fld">Venue</label>
          <div class="seg" id="rVenue"><button data-v="N" class="on">Neutral</button><button data-v="H">Home adv</button></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn gold mt" id="applyRes" style="width:100%">Apply &amp; recalculate Elo</button>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>History <span style="float:right;color:var(--muted2);font-weight:400;font-family:var(--mono)" id="histCount"></span></h3>
      <div class="hist" id="histBox"></div>
      <button class="btn ghost sm mt" id="undoRes" style="display:none">↶ Undo last result</button>
      <button class="btn ghost sm mt danger" id="clearRes" style="display:none">Clear all &amp; reset Elo</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MODEL -->
  <section id="v-model" class="view">
    <div class="panel" style="margin-top:0">
      <h3>Model calibration</h3>
      <label class="fld">Total expected goals (&mu;)</label>
      <div class="range"><input id="muR" type="range" min="2.0" max="3.2" step="0.05" value="2.6"><span class="val" id="muV">2.60</span></div>
      <label class="fld mt">Elo-to-supremacy divisor</label>
      <div class="range"><input id="divR" type="range" min="100" max="220" step="5" value="160"><span class="val" id="divV">160</span></div>
      <label class="fld mt">Home advantage (Elo pts)</label>
      <div class="range"><input id="advR" type="range" min="0" max="150" step="5" value="100"><span class="val" id="advV">100</span></div>
      <button class="btn ghost sm mt" id="resetModel">Reset to defaults</button>
    </div>
    <details open>
      <summary>How the maths works</summary>
      <p><b style="color:var(--chalk)">Elo expectation.</b> dr = EloA − EloB (+home adj). Expected score We = 1 / (10^(−dr/400) + 1) — the same curve eloratings.net uses.</p>
      <p><b style="color:var(--chalk)">Goals.</b> Supremacy = clamp(dr, ±480) / divisor. λA = μ/2 + sup/2, λB = μ/2 − sup/2 (floored at 0.35). Defaults are tuned so win-share tracks the raw Elo expectation. Lower the divisor to make favourites stronger.</p>
      <p><b style="color:var(--chalk)">Markets.</b> Independent Poisson on each λ builds an 11×11 scoreline grid; W/D/L, correct scores, O/U and BTTS are all summed from it.</p>
      <p><b style="color:var(--chalk)">Knockout.</b> Draw mass is split to "advance" by a 50/50 shootout. Market lines stay on 90 minutes.</p>
      <p><b style="color:var(--chalk)">Recalculation.</b> Logging a result updates both teams: change = K · G · (W − We), where G is the goal-difference multiplier (1 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 1.75+(n−3)/8) and K is the match weight.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted2)">Not affiliated with eloratings.net or FIFA. A model is a tool, not a tip — stake to your own judgement.</p>
    </details>
  </section>
</div>

<nav class="tabs" id="tabs">
  <button data-t="lab" class="on"><span class="ic">⊞</span>Match Lab</button>
  <button data-t="groups"><span class="ic">≣</span>Groups</button>
  <button data-t="ratings"><span class="ic">↕</span>Ratings</button>
  <button data-t="results"><span class="ic">●</span>Results</button>
  <button data-t="model"><span class="ic">∿</span>Model</button>
</nav>
<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

